    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <description><![CDATA[A beautiful client for Plex & Jellyfin

Stream your media library with HDR, Dolby Vision, offline downloads, and a gorgeous experience across all your devices.

**Features**

- Wide Codec Support
- HDR10+
- Subtitles
- Cross-Platform
- Offline
- Watch Together
- Tracker Sync
- Skip intros
- Chapter support
- Gestures
]]></description>
    <summary>A modern client for Plex and Jellyfin on desktop, mobile, and TV. Built with Flutter for native performance and a clean interface.</summary>
    <releaseNotes><![CDATA[[Releases](https://github.com/edde746/plezy/releases)

## Fixed

- Jellyfin home screen offline loops
- Playback crashes on older Android and Fire OS devices
- Back navigation on media and catalog details
- Music volume persistence and mini-player interactions
- D-pad volume and sync sliders
- Keyboard shortcut recording
- Live TV guide long-press actions and recording sheets
- Watch Together leave and end-session actions

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/edde746/plezy/compare/2.9.0...2.9.1]]></releaseNotes>
